4Geeks Academy offers a Data Science & Machine Learning course. In just 16 weeks, students will learn Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics. They will become professional Data Analysts, capable of contributing to any data-driven team. The course covers creating predictive models using libraries like Pandas and Numpy, exploring algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees, and working with supervised and unsupervised learning models. Students will also practice solving real-life cases and develop their own AI projects. The course is available in English or Spanish and includes three classes per week with a maximum class size of 12 people. Upon completion, students receive a recognized certificate. For more information, visit the website: [4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning).stop